'''enamine'''
#{{chemistry}} any of a class of [[unsaturated]] [[nitrogen]] [[compound]]s, having the [[general formula]] R<sub>2</sub>C=C(R)-NR<sub>2</sub>, prepared by the [[condensation reaction]] of an [[aldehyde]] or [[ketone]] with an [[secondary amine]]; they are the [[tautomeric]] forms of [[imine]]s